FROM rust:1.78-alpine AS chef
RUN cargo install cargo-chef
WORKDIR /app

FROM chef AS planner
COPY Cargo.toml Cargo.lock ./
RUN cargo chef prepare --recipe-path recipe.json

FROM rust:1.78-alpine AS rust-builder
RUN apk add --no-cache musl-dev python3-dev
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=planner /app/recipe.json recipe.json
RUN cargo install cargo-chef && \
    cargo chef cook --release --recipe-path recipe.json
COPY server/ ./server/
COPY Cargo.toml Cargo.lock ./
RUN cargo build --release

FROM python:3.11-slim-bookworm AS python-builder
RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    build-essential \
    git && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
RUN python -m venv /opt/venv
ENV PATH="/opt/venv/bin:$PATH"
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir --upgrade pip && \
    pip install --no-cache-dir \
    torch==2.1.2 \
    torchvision==0.16.2 \
    torchaudio==2.1.2 \
    transformers==4.36.2 \
    tokenizers==0.14.1 \
    safetensors==0.4.1

FROM debian:bookworm-slim AS runtime
RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    curl \
    ca-certificates \
    libssl3 && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* && \
    groupadd -r inference && \
    useradd -r -g inference -u 1000 inference
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=rust-builder /app/target/release/inference-server /usr/local/bin/inference-server
COPY --from=python-builder /opt/venv /opt/venv
ENV PATH="/opt/venv/bin:$PATH" \
    PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1
USER inference
EXPOSE 8080
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=10s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8080/health || exit 1
LABEL maintainer="inference-team@example.com" \
      org.opencontainers.image.description="Rust + Python ML Inference Server" \
      org.opencontainers.image.source="https://github.com/org/repo"
CMD ["/usr/local/bin/inference-server", "--port", "8080"]
